Metadata: California Sea Grant Fisheries Newsletter (Winter, Spring, and Summer 2005)

Quarterly newsletter of the California Sea Grant Extension Program and UC Division of Agriculture and Natural Resources. Topics of interest include: Nelson nabbed for Northern fisheries position; California Sea Grant Commission; California Department of Fish and Game Marine Life Management Act research projects; New Sea Grant marine Fisheries research projects; Dewees sabbatical project; Update on collaborative nearshore fish project.
